text: Equanimeous Tristan Imhotep J. St. Brown (born September 30, 1996) is an American football wide receiver for the Chicago Bears of the National Football League (NFL). He played college football at Notre Dame and was drafted by the Green Bay Packers in the sixth round of the 2018 NFL Draft. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:American football wide receivers Category:Chicago Bears players Category:Green Bay Packers players
